  "course_description": "This course introduces students to the fundamentals of AWS cloud computing and AI services. It covers essential AWS services like EC2, S3, Lambda, and SageMaker, as well as AWS security, identity management, and global infrastructure. Students will also explore AI, ML, and generative AI concepts, focusing on responsible use and practical applications. The course will prepare students for two different AWS Certifications.",
